ave Rafe and Kaden, I wonder which one is the Prince. :) I loved them both but one more than the other. Swoon. Lol. There are other characters in the book that play good characters and bad characters. I thought they were all well played out. One of Lia's brothers, Walther, puts in a couple of appearances as well. I loved him! \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThere was a really sad part almost half-way through the book \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg alt=\" \" src=\"https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1497887569ra/23065914.gif\" class=\"gr-hostedUserImg\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAnd right at the end, an even more heartbreaking moment. I really hope Lia gets them all! She's strong, she can do this!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMY BLOG: \u003ca href=\"http://melissa413readsalot.blogspot.com/2017/06/the-kiss-of-deception-by-mary-e-pearson.html\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eMelissa Martin's Reading List\u003c/a\u003e","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/17438949?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"own","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/17438949?shelf=own"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"fantasy-all","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/17438949?shelf=fantasy-all"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1281027252"},"likeCount":202,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":32,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.XdcPvgmTipUAk_Qd02AXJg":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.XdcPvgmTipUAk_Qd02AXJg","__typename":"Work","legacyId":22617247,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.Ci5T78TFw0MT_9QE6KNOxw"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/22617247-the-kiss-of-deception","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/22617247-